<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Beranda - Pemesanan Tiket Kereta Api</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/home.css">
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        }
        .navbar {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            background-color: #007bff;
            color: white;
        }
        .navbar img.logo {
            height: 50px;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }
        .navbar-title {
            margin-left: 10px;
            font-size: 20px;
        }
        nav a {
            margin: 0 10px;
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        nav a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }
        .hero {
            background: url('/kereta-bg.jpg') no-repeat center center;
            background-size: cover;
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 80px 20px;
        }
        .hero-content h1 {
            font-size: 32px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .hero-content p {
            font-size: 18px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .btn-primary {
            background-color: #ffcc00;
            padding: 12px 30px;
            color: black;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-decoration: none;
            cursor: pointer;
        }
        .btn-primary:hover {
            background-color: #e6b800;
        }
        .features {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-around;
            padding: 40px 20px;
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
        }
        .feature {
            text-align: center;
            width: 30%;
        }
        .feature h3 a {
            text-decoration: none;
            color: #007bff;
        }
        .feature h3 a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }
        .feature p {
            font-size: 16px;
            margin-top: 10px;
        }
        .footer {
            background-color: #333;
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 10px 0;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header class="navbar">
        <div class="navbar-left">
            <img src="/logo-kai.jpg" alt="Logo KAI" class="logo">
            <h1 class="navbar-title">Kereta Api Indonesia</h1>
        </div>
        <nav>
            <a href="/home">Beranda</a>
            <a href="/booking">Pesan Tiket</a>
            <a href="/" class="btn-logout">Logout</a>
        </nav>        
    </header>

    <main>
        <section class="hero">
            <div class="hero-content">
                <h1>Selamat Datang di Pemesanan Tiket Kereta Api</h1>
                <p>Pesan tiket perjalanan Anda dengan mudah dan cepat.</p>
                <a href="/booking" class="btn-primary">Pesan Tiket Sekarang</a>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="features">
            <div class="feature">
                <h3><a href="/proses-mudah">Proses Mudah</a></h3>
                <p>Cukup 3 langkah untuk memesan tiket Anda.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature">
                <h3><a href="/jadwal-lengkap">Jadwal Lengkap</a></h3>
                <p>Tersedia jadwal perjalanan dari berbagai rute.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature">
                <h3><a href="/aman-dan-cepat">Aman dan Cepat</a></h3>
                <p>Transaksi Anda terjamin aman dan cepat.</p>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>
    
    <footer class="footer">
        <div class="footer-content">
            <p>Kelompok 3: Elwin Pranata N 022, Ihsan Putra R 041, Ryan Syaputra MA 025, Haris Shihab D 015</p>
        </div>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>
